Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Expedite Request Denied
body: On June 1, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190132981. We do not believe, based on a review of your request, that your case meets one or more of the expedite criteria and otherwise merits expedited processing. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director. Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Delivered To Me By The Post Office
body: On June 8, 2021, the Post Office delivered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190132982, to the address that you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708407840368. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
